Package: m6AnetAnalyzer
Title: Downstream Analysis Tools for m6Anet Output
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hanna", "Lee", , "hannalee809@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for downstream analysis of m6Anet output from Nanopore direct RNA sequencing experiments. The package supports quality control, transcript-level summarization of m6A methylation using weighted modification ratios, integration with gene expression data, and comparative analyses across experimental conditions. Functions are designed to facilitate interpretation of m6A modification patterns without requiring extensive custom scripting.
